	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />There's always just PCs and emulators.  Any PC (486 or better with VGA) can emulate the NES, but it won't be a native 6502 system for tinkering on the native hardware.  It would still just be in a sandbox.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


